            <div class="row">

                <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-12">
                    <div id="about" class="tabcontent">
                        <h1 class="font-weight-bold mb-4">India’s cheapest hotel booking platform for price first travelers.</h1>

                        <p>You book hotels online. You compare prices. You want the lowest one. Many platforms show different prices for the same room on the same date. You spend time checking multiple sites. You still feel unsure about your decision.</p>

                        <p>Book My Hotels exists to solve this.</p>

                        <p>We focus on one outcome. You see the lowest available hotel price clearly. You compare. You book. You move on.</p>



                        <h4 class="mt-5">What We Do</h4>

                        <p>We help you:</p>

                        <ul>
                            <li>Compare real hotel prices across cities in India</li>
                            <li>Find budget and affordable stays</li>
                            <li>Book at the lowest available rate</li>
                        </ul>

                        <p>You do not need complicated features. You need price clarity. You need confidence before you pay.</p>



                        <h4 class="mt-5">Why We Focus on Price</h4>

                        <p>India is a price sensitive market. Most hotel bookings fall in the budget and mid range segments. Small price differences influence decisions. When you travel for work, family visits, or short trips, you track every rupee.</p>

                        <p>Large platforms often prioritize sponsored listings and promotions. Paid placements appear first. Price comparison becomes harder.</p>

                        <p>We take a different route. We prioritize price first discovery. You see options sorted by cost. You decide based on value.</p>



                        <h4 class="mt-5">Built for Budget Travelers</h4>

                        <p>You travel for many reasons:</p>

                        <ul>
                            <li>Business trips</li>
                            <li>Family events</li>
                            <li>Weekend stays</li>
                            <li>Last minute bookings</li>
                        </ul>

                        <p>In each case, your priority stays the same. You want a comfortable room at the lowest possible price.</p>

                        <p>Book My Hotels focuses on budget and affordable hotels across India. We keep the experience simple. Clear listings. Clear pricing. Direct booking.</p>



                        <h4 class="mt-5">Our Mission</h4>

                        <p>Our mission is direct. Make hotel bookings cheaper and more transparent for you.</p>

                        <p>We do not aim to offer everything. We aim to own one promise. When you want the cheapest hotel option, you check Book My Hotels first.</p>



                        <h4 class="mt-5">Your Decision</h4>

                        <p>If the room is the same and the date is the same, your decision comes down to price.</p>

                        <p>
                            <strong>Book with clarity.</strong><br>
                            <strong>Book with confidence.</strong><br>
                            <strong>Book with Book My Hotels.</strong>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Since our inception in 2022, our mission has been to empower travellers to move beyond the limitations of an oversaturated market. We aim to bring a fresh perspective to travel, offering the flexibility and freedom every traveller deserves.</p>


